articles.author: Hannah Mcdonald
articles.title: Zelensky lands in Balkan Europe: President's whirlwind trip sees war-time leader fly to Greece - after Denmark - Daily Mail
articles.description: President Zelensky met with Greek Prime Minister Kyriakos Mitsotakis, and also was scheduled to meet the country's figurehead president, Katerina Sakellaropoulou.
articles.content:
President Volodymyr Zelensky has flown to Greece for talks with the country's leadership after Denmark and the Netherlands vowed to send F-16 fighter jets to Ukraine.
